      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON CHINOOK (1) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 2 lengths (29.82) behind Chuck A Party at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can measure up this time. BOMB ROCKY (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the money last time though when second (23.70) at this track. Solid record here winning five races. Has performed well from this box with a win and seven minor placings to her name from 14 starts. Can measure up. KIA KEEPING (7) goes very well this course and distance starting 17 times for six wins and four minors. Placed last time (43.59) at Angle Park in a Special conditions race, finishing second and beaten 6 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. WAY COOL (6) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
